ChangeGVBuffer.Script:
var input = environment.get("input_toupper");
var output = environment.get("output_toupper");
data.setProperty("INPUT_TOUPPER", input != null ? "OK" : "KO");
data.setProperty("OUTPUT_TOUPPER", output != null ? "OK" : "KO");

ResultProcessor.Script:
var str = "";
for (var i=0; i<results.size(); i++)
{
    var inV = results.get(i).getInput().getObject();
    var outV = results.get(i).getOutput().getObject();
    str += ";[" + inV + " -> " + outV + "]";
}

data.setObject(str.substring(1));

